---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Code Snippets & Techniques — Max Burkhardt">
  <article class="page">
    <header class="header">
      <h1>Code Snippets &amp; Techniques</h1>
      <p>
        A place to break down how I implemented specific gameplay features, with code and notes.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="block">
      <h2>Example: Mass‑based Movement Speed</h2>
      <p>
        In this prototype, the player’s movement speed scales with their current mass.
        This keeps the character feeling heavy when they collect more mass.
      </p>

      <pre><code class="language-csharp">{`// Adjust speed based on current mass
        float baseSpeed = 6f;
        float massFactor = Mathf.Clamp(currentMass / maxMass, 0.5f, 1.5f);
        float moveSpeed = baseSpeed * massFactor;`}</code></pre>

      <p>
        The mass factor is clamped so the player never becomes too slow or too fast,
        while still giving a noticeable change in feel.
      </p>

      <img
        src="/snippets/mass-diagram.png"
        alt="Diagram showing mass and speed relationship"
        class="inline-image"
      />
    </section>

    <section class="block">
      <h2>How to add more snippets</h2>
      <p>
        Just copy this block, change the title, text, and code. You don’t need to touch any
        Astro or collections – this is a normal page.
      </p>
    </section>

    
  </article>

  <style>
    .page {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 2.5rem 2rem 3.5rem;
    }

    .header h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .header p {
      max-width: 40rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .block {
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .block h2 {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    }

    .block p {
      line-height: 1.7;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    }

    pre {
      margin: 1rem 0;
      padding: 0.75rem 0.9rem;
      border-radius: 6px;
      background: #020617;
      overflow-x: auto;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
    }

    code {
      font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas,
        "Liberation Mono", "Courier New", monospace;
    }

    :root[data-theme="light"] pre,
    [data-theme="light"] pre {
      background: #111827;
      color: #f9fafb;
    }

    .inline-image {
      max-width: 100%;
      border-radius: 8px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
    }
  </style>
</Layout>